Diamond::
She got up and walked out of the pod. She loked at the ground for a 
moment. For one second, she wished she had led a different life. But 
this one, killing, was the only life she had ever know. She smiled 
with a slight evil twist in it. "I'll get you guys some quaters and 
get you settled in. Then you can meet up with KitKat, the leader of 
our group."
